### 5c Cross-perspective question set (preliminary)

Proposed common questions (subject to refinement after ratification):
- Q1. Is warrant-firing genuinely sparse by design, or is it under-articulated?
- Q2. Do observational-session metrics (no-growth streaks; preservation depths; zero-event windows) constitute evidence of discipline working, evidence of discipline deferring, or neither?
